title: congreso coalition negotiation
on-arrival: {!
    Q.congreso_coalition_leverage = 2
    Q.congreso_coalition_negotiated_reform = 0;
    Q.congreso_coalition_negotiated_amnesty = 0;
    Q.congreso_coalition_negotiated_funding = 0;
    Q.congreso_coalition_negotiated_cash = 0;
    Q.congreso_coalition_negotiated_renfe = 0;
    Q.congreso_coalition_negotiated_ports = 0;
    Q.congreso_coalition_negotiated_education = 0;
    Q.congreso_coalition_negotiated_police = 0;
    Q.congreso_coalition_negotiated_borders = 0;
!}
go-to: choices
# TODO: dynamic leverage?
# TODO: judiciary reform?

@choices
new-page: true
on-arrival: {!
    Q.congreso_coalition_negotiated_any = 0;
    if (Q.congreso_coalition_negotiated_reform || Q.congreso_coalition_negotiated_amnesty || Q.congreso_coalition_negotiated_funding || Q.congreso_coalition_negotiated_cash || Q.congreso_coalition_negotiated_renfe || Q.congreso_coalition_negotiated_ports || Q.congreso_coalition_negotiated_education || Q.congreso_coalition_negotiated_police || Q.congreso_coalition_negotiated_borders) {
        Q.congreso_coalition_negotiated_any = 1;
    }
!}


= Coalition Negotiations

A potential [+ congreso_coalition_lead_party +]-led Gobierno requires our support in the Congreso for the investiture to go through. 

[? if congreso_coalition_negotiated_any: So far, we have demanded: ?]

[? if congreso_coalition_negotiated_funding: - [? if congreso_left_carrier == congreso_coalition_lead_party: A revision of the Catalan economic regime, as a part of the planned Consitutional reform.?][? if congreso_coalition_lead_party = "psoe": A negotiation for a new "singular" economic regime for Catalonia, as a part of a revision of the autonomic financing system. ?]?]

[? if congreso_coalition_negotiated_reform: - That the planned reform of the Constitution includes provisions for further decentralization. ?]

[? if congreso_coalition_negotiated_renfe: - For Catalonia to fully control its railway network. ?]

[? if congreso_coalition_negotiated_ports: - For Catalonia to fully control its ports and airports. ?]

[? if congreso_coalition_negotiated_education: - For Catalonia to have complete independence in Education policies. ?]

[? if congreso_coalition_negotiated_police: - For the Mossos d'Esquadra to be the only police force in Catalonia. ?]

[? if congreso_coalition_negotiated_borders: - For Catalonia to have its own policy and enforcement over Immigration and Border control. ?]

[? if congreso_coalition_negotiated_amnesty: - A General Amnesty Law for all political prisoners. ?]

[? if congreso_coalition_negotiated_cash and public_debt > 10: - A forgiveness of a part of the Generalitat's debt.?]
[? if congreso_coalition_negotiated_cash and public_debt <= 10: - Further Gobierno-covered investment in Catalonia.?]

- @funding
- @cash
- @devolution
- @const_reform
- @amnesty
- @funding_dump
- @cash_dump
- @devolution_dump
- @const_reform_dump
- @amnesty_dump
- @resolve


@funding
title: Demand a reform of the economic regime of Catalonia. 
subtitle: Catalonia has been systemically underfunded. [? if congreso_left_carrier == congreso_coalition_lead_party: A reform by [+ congreso_left_carrier +] may be folded into their broader plans for Constitutional reform. ?][? if congreso_coalition_lead_party = "psoe": The PSOE seems open to talk about a "singular" regime and a revision of that system. ?]
choose-if: (congreso_left_carrier == congreso_coalition_lead_party or congreso_coalition_lead_party == "psoe") and congreso_coalition_leverage > 0 and not congreso_coalition_negotiated_funding
unavailable-subtitle: [? if congreso_left_carrier != congreso_coalition_lead_party and congreso_coalition_lead_party != "psoe": The [+ congreso_left_carrier +] has no intention of touching the autonomic financing system. ?][? if congreso_coalition_negotiated_funding: This is already in our demands list. ?][? if congreso_coalition_leverage < 1 and not congreso_coalition_negotiated_funding: We lack leverage to demand this, on top of the rest we've already asked for. ?]
on-arrival: congreso_coalition_negotiated_funding = 1; congreso_coalition_leverage -= 1;
go-to: choices

@funding_dump
title: Maybe we don't need to rethink the finances of Catalonia
view-if: congreso_coalition_negotiated_funding
choose-if: congreso_coalition_negotiated_funding
on-arrival: congreso_coalition_negotiated_funding = 0; congreso_coalition_leverage += 1;
go-to: choices

@cash
title: Demand extra state-side economic support for Catalonia
subtitle: This could take the form of more Gobierno-covered investment in Catalonia or a forgiveness of a part of the Generalitat's debt.
choose-if: congreso_coalition_leverage > 0 and not congreso_coalition_negotiated_cash
unavailable-subtitle:[? if congreso_coalition_negotiated_cash: This is already in our demands list. ?][? if congreso_coalition_leverage < 1 and not congreso_coalition_negotiated_cash: We lack leverage to demand this, on top of the rest we've already asked for. ?]
on-arrival: congreso_coalition_negotiated_cash = 1; congreso_coalition_leverage -= 1;
go-to: choices

@cash_dump
title: Maybe we don't the Gobierno to assist in Catalan finances
view-if: congreso_coalition_negotiated_cash
choose-if: congreso_coalition_negotiated_cash
on-arrival: congreso_coalition_negotiated_cash = 0; congreso_coalition_negotiated_cash += 1;
go-to: choices

@devolution
title: Demand an expansion of Catalonia's governance powers
choose-if: congreso_coalition_leverage > 0
unavailable-subtitle: We lack leverage to demand this, on top of the rest we've already asked for.
subtitle: We could push for many different concessions here.

There's still a myriad of competences and concessions related to regional powers we could demand for Catalonia.

- @renfe
- @ports_airports
- @universities
- @military
- @borders
- @choices: Go back

@renfe
title: Complete railway control
subtitle: State-owned RENFE and ADIF still operate and control a big part of the Catalan railway network after all. 
view-if: not competence_renfe
choose-if: congreso_coalition_leverage > 0 and not congreso_coalition_negotiated_renfe and not competence_renfe
unavailable-subtitle:[? if congreso_coalition_negotiated_renfe: This is already in our demands list. ?][? if congreso_coalition_leverage < 1 and not congreso_coalition_negotiated_renfe: We lack leverage to demand this, on top of the rest we've already asked for. ?]
on-arrival: congreso_coalition_negotiated_renfe = 1; congreso_coalition_leverage -= 1;
go-to: choices

@ports_airports
title: Governance over Ports and Airports
subtitle: Right now only minor ones are controlled by the Generalitat.
view-if: not competence_ports
choose-if: congreso_coalition_leverage > 0 and not congreso_coalition_negotiated_ports and not competence_ports
unavailable-subtitle:[? if congreso_coalition_negotiated_ports: This is already in our demands list. ?][? if congreso_coalition_leverage < 1 and not congreso_coalition_negotiated_ports: We lack leverage to demand this, on top of the rest we've already asked for. ?]
on-arrival: congreso_coalition_negotiated_ports = 1; congreso_coalition_leverage -= 1;
go-to: choices

@universities
title: Complete governance on Education
subtitle: Universities are still a shared competence, and Catalan education laws are usually struck down or limited by Spanish Courts.
view-if: not competence_education
choose-if: congreso_coalition_leverage > 0 and not congreso_coalition_negotiated_education and not competence_education
unavailable-subtitle:[? if congreso_coalition_negotiated_education: This is already in our demands list. ?][? if congreso_coalition_leverage < 1 and not congreso_coalition_negotiated_education: We lack leverage to demand this, on top of the rest we've already asked for. ?]
on-arrival: congreso_coalition_negotiated_education = 1; congreso_coalition_leverage -= 1;
go-to: choices

@military
