unavailable-subtitle: [? if congreso_left_carrier != congreso_coalition_lead_party and congreso_coalition_lead_party != "psoe": The [+ congreso_coalition_lead_party +] has already ruled this out. ?][? if congreso_coalition_negotiated_borders: This is already in our demands list. ?][? if congreso_coalition_leverage < 1 and not congreso_coalition_negotiated_borders: We lack leverage to demand this, on top of the rest we've already asked for. ?]
